<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>bust one’s balls • bust someone’s balls</xh5><p> <i>bust one’s balls</i>—(coarse sl.; used of men) work extremely hard to accomplish smth.: I have only two days until the examination, so I have to <u>bust my balls</u> if I don’t want to fail.</p><p><i>bust someone’s balls</i>—(coarse sl.) 1. make fun of or tease a man: Everybody in the classroom <u>bust Tom’s balls</u> about his bald head. 2. <i>(of a woman)</i> ridicule a man; hurt a man’s feelings: Janet has a bad habit; she loves to <u>bust a man’s balls</u> if he tries to flirt with her.</p></entry>
